FuncDef: This command creates a VLAN range or enters the context of the specified VLAN ranges for configuration applicable to that range of VLANs.

ParaDef.Info: Specifies the start of the VLAN range. Values-0 to 4096. ParamDefault: Default- 200
Specifies the end of VLAN range. Values-0 to 4096. ParamDefault: Default- 400
Specifies to use defaults for the interface.
